  "verse_id": "4.33",
  "mūla": {
    "devanāgarī": "श्रेयान् द्रव्य-मयाद् यज्ञाज् ज्ञान-यज्ञः परन्तप | सर्वं कर्माखिलं पार्थ ज्ञाने परिसमाप्यते",
    "iast": "śreyān dravya-mayād yajñāj jñāna-yajñaḥ parantapa | sarvaṃ karmākhilaṃ pārtha jñāne parisamāpyate",
    "chapter_position": "Chapter 4 (Jñāna-Karma-Sannyāsa-Yoga (The Yoga of Renunciation of Action in Knowledge)), verse 33",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "addressed_to": "Arjuna"
  },
